  "title": "Beautician",
  "description": "<h2>Beautician（美容师）— （Paragon, Orchard）</h2><p><br /><strong>Salary:</strong> SGD 2,200 – 4,500（月薪 + 提成 + 奖金，视经验而定）<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> 5–6 days/week（包含周末；具体排班可安排）</p><h3>Job Description</h3><p>We are looking for a skilled and customer-focused <strong>Beautician</strong> to join our team at Shugar Prestige (Paragon). You will provide professional facial and beauty treatments, maintain service excellence, and support customer retention.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Provide facial treatments (cleansing, extraction, mask, basic skincare routine)</p></li><li><p>Operate beauty equipment (training provided if needed)</p></li><li><p>Skin analysis and recommend suitable treatment plans/products</p></li><li><p>Maintain treatment room hygiene and comply with SOP/NEA standards</p></li><li><p>Deliver excellent customer service and aftercare advice</p></li><li><p>Support sales of packages/products with professional consultation (non-hard sell)</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Relevant experience in facial / beauty / aesthetics preferred</p></li><li><p>Certified in beauty therapy / CIDESCO / CIBTAC / ITEC is an advantage (not compulsory)</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills; able to speak basic English (Mandarin is a plus)</p></li><li><p>Positive attitude, service-minded, responsible, and willing to learn</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends/public holidays (rotational)</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Attractive commission & performance bonus (KPI clear, can earn one)</p></li><li><p>Training and upgrade opportunities (product + equipment)</p></li><li><p>Friendly team culture, supportive management</p></li><li><p>Convenient location (Orchard MRT / Paragon)</p></li></ul><h3>How to Apply</h3><p><strong>WhatsApp : </strong>+65 9858 0286</p>",
